                <Gloss>concern for</Gloss>
                <Gloss>care of</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>Though one might regard ἐπίστασις as meaning only the position of authority, nevertheless this authority is expressed in terms of the oversight and care of others. In a sense the meaning of ἐπίστασις in {S:04701102800010} is defined by the following appositional phrase, ἡ μέριμνα πασῶν τῶν ἐκκλησιῶν ‘concern for all the churches.’ For another interpretation of ἐπίστασις in {S:04701102800010}, see {D:25.239}.</Comments>
